nodes.text: Cay Ploon Kett was an individual who, approximately four years before the Battle of Yavin, was imprisoned along with many others by the Galactic Empire.

The name "Cay Ploon Kett" first appeared in "Rebel Resolve," the twelfth episode of the first season of Star Wars Rebels. Strikingly similar to "K. Plunkett," the name was written in Aurebesh in a prisoner data file.
